{"tid":1223670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先剛剛去完金鐘，嘗試搵嗰啲絕食人士，睇下佢哋搞成點...","createTime":"2019-06-14T18:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T10:54:21.000Z","uid":259666,"like":111,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9158db8e02ffa7847cbbe4bed95c844617827a09","tid":1223670,"uid":259666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"22:40 - 去到金鐘，出地鐵站上海富中心，見到一堆耶穌門徒喺天橋上面，唱緊聖詩，大概幾百個信眾。行入去望望，原來通常聽聖詩，要加埋講耶穌，前後大概半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。當中企前面果幾個唱得非常投入，甚至舉高雙手好似被召喚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...但係我都尊重佢地既誠意既。行返出嚟嗰陣，沿途見到好多口號既紙張貼左係牆上面，其中有一個紙皮上面寫住絕食，但係冇人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n23:15 - 聽完聖詩，行返出嚟再周圍問人，都冇乜人知班絕食人士去咗邊，之後行埋去添馬公園，見到人數少啲，三五成群咁樣。中間有急救站、資源站等等。但係都見唔到絕食者...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n23:40 - 正想放棄之際，行到去天橋上面準備返金鐘地鐵站，見到有位女士喺度鬧緊啲差人，有少少似飲醉酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以去八卦下。之後就望到有人，貼出「探訪絕食」嘅紙張。一問之下，原來就係前面。但係原來要比差人溝通一輪先至可以入去...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n23:55 - 經過一輪遊說，又東又西，差人話每次只可以10個入去，中間又再拖一拖，最後出現負責同「傳媒溝通」嘅警方，再溝通一輪，前後搞左十幾二十分鐘，先至放行...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n00:20 - 入面大概有八至九位絕食者，有啲瞓緊覺、有啲仲清醒，當中女仔佔多，男士得兩位。同其中一位靚靚港女傾左一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，講返出面發生緊啲咩事，例如建制派開始坳底、今日林鄭個記者會又開唔成、嗰班支持送終嘅記者會亦都收咗皮。傾談間，見到嗰個佢都真係有啲攰，但係佢對眼都仲係有神，意志堅定。我係咁話多謝佢，反而佢安慰我，話大家都係為香港人，感動到想喊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話想托我話俾大家連登巴絲知，話佢哋都安好，大家唔使擔心，唔駛大家狗衝探佢地，因為堅係有啲攰，而且已經有好多物資。如無意外，應該會星期日朝頭早完成絕食，佢仲話星期日出嚟遊行。我就叫佢小心身體，休息下，等我哋幫佢行啦⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望大家睇完之後，星期日一定要出嚟，<strong>唔好嘥咗佢既一番努力同心機</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fAKmdHC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfAKmdHC.png&h=fcc238ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6sfh9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6sfh9i.png&h=e00d7f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwXOC9j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwXOC9j.png&h=d014f632&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtAkuf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtAkuf0.png&h=47e9f78b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBc3r2F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBc3r2F.png&h=389839de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBWf2A1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBWf2A1.png&h=7a764c16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f51a9f068eec30c2e8c98131d70520bdcadab0c3","tid":1223670,"uid":259666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"052c688d872d198a4c76e7b585f61383612754ac","tid":1223670,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c32e6fc3fdc753f10ceed5f9eecfba62c6a05e9","tid":1223670,"uid":260870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:23:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037d5421a34fe782cd462b1afbcdd9dc61cb07e4","tid":1223670,"uid":137046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:25:12.000Z","msg":"加油!!推!!"},{"pid":"f5c6e41c665a63d46ba02695687f7086abdeda4e","tid":1223670,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"